3.title: Yeh Hai Mohabbatein
3.description: Based on Manju Kapoor's Custody, this is the story of Raman and Ishita, brought together by destiny and their love for Ruhi, Raman's daughter from his ex-wife.

81.title: Diya Aur Baati
81.description: Sooraj, a loving husband and a self-made man from a traditional family helps his ambitious wife, Sandhya achieve her dreams of becoming an IPS officer.

152.title: IPKKND Ek Baar Phir
152.description: Destiny brings free-spirited Astha and chauvinistic Shlok together. Soon Astha learns that not all is as rosy as it seems in Shlok’s perfect family.

358.title: Arjun
358.description: Meet Arjun, a rebel-cop and the lead of the Emergency Task Force who doesn't mind going the extra mile to ensure justice, even if it takes breaking rules.

423.title: Iss Pyar Ko Kya Naam
423.description: A perfect story of opposites attract, where Khushi, a simple girl and Arnav, an arrogant businessman realise that they cannot live without each other.

435.title: Mahabharat
435.description: The mother of all wars, the epitome of all rivalries, the cauldron of emotions, insecurities, jealousies, and power play - Mahabharat!

527.title: Ek Hazaaron Mein
527.description: Sisters Maanvi and Jeevika can go to any lengths for each other. Follow the sisters’ journey as they stand by each other and find their soulmates.

586.title: Yeh Rishta
586.description: A personal tragedy creates a rift in Abhimanyu and Akshara’s marital life. Years later, when destiny offers a second chance, will the duo embrace love?

693.title: Saathiya 2
693.description: A few years after Anant's death, Gehna has completely turned her life around. In this new journey, will she finally find her perfect partner?

9567.title: Ishqbaaz
9567.description: Brothers Shivaay, Omkara and Rudra share an unbreakable bond despite their dysfunctional family. What happens when cupid strikes each of them?

10655.title: Naamkarann
10655.description: An illegitimate child, Avni sets out to create an identity for herself amidst numerous hurdles created by her own grandmother, Dayavanti.

18293.title: Nazar
18293.description: Apurva lives under the constant threat of his sister, Mohini, a Daayan. Unaware that he is a Daavansh himself, what will happen when he discovers his powers?

1260003582.title: Divya-Drishti
1260003582.description: Separated at childhood, Divya and Drishti attain super powers to see and manipulate future. But their own future lies in the hands of a Pisachini.

1260011873.title: Yehh Jadu Hai Jinn Ka
1260011873.description: He lives under the shadow of a djinn while she is blessed with angelic qualities. What turn will Aman and Roshni's life take when the two fall in love?

1260015192.title: Yeh Hai Chahatein
1260015192.description: All that remains constant is love! When a renowned rockstar Samrat crosses paths with an introverted Nayantara, an unconventional love story comes to life.

1260022017.title: Anupama
1260022017.description: Despite the many challenges thrown her way, Anupama begins a new chapter of her life post-divorce. Head held always high, what's waiting for her next?

1260043179.title: Ghum Hai Kisikey
1260043179.description: Retreating from tragedy, Virat ties the knot with Pakhi to initiate new beginnings. Years later, when Sai returns, he is forced to question his choices.

1260048110.title: Imlie
1260048110.description: The saga continues! Imlie and Chini grow up as strong and independent women but differ in personalities. Will their sisterly bond prevail amid the ego clash?

1260103747.title: Aashiqana
1260103747.description: NEW EPISODES FROM MON-SAT. A roaring rampage of revenge! Terror reigns the city as masked maniacs wreak carnage. Can Yash and Chikki put an end to this nightmare?

1260121083.title: Faltu
1260121083.description: What’s in a name? Amid the arid landscape of Rajasthan, a dreamy-eyed young woman battles to prove her mettle whilst navigating through cultural stereotypes.
